am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Agro/taunt</span><hr size=1> Ok this is a Wurmslayer post. I really hesitate to even start it cause I know its been beat to death, but I just thought I would share this and see if anyone has anything constructive to tell me... so here it goes.<br>
<br>
I am lvl 41 now, dwarf warrior, and yes, I'm using Wurmslayer and a Dwarven Sap/Yak (whichever I feel like at the moment) and an FBSS. I have really enjoyed the Wurm so far, and it has worked very well for me and my cleric friend.  I usually use the Wurmslayer cause we have definitely noticed a huge difference in the time it takes to kill something (over using 2 lower damage faster delay weapons). I must admit that that difference seems to be getting smaller and smaller, and its getting to the point where its almost even.  I know I am entering that borderline area where things like a Jade mace will out damage the Wurm per minute (course you have to acutually get one first =).<br>
<br>
Okay, so we were in Sol B the other night with my friend, and we had a lvl 33 monk guildie along with us just cause he was bored. We were just in the window/pool area and I thought since we had 2 tanks I would use the Sap (main) and Yak(offh). Well with this combo the monk would consistently pull agro off me almost every fight. As soon as I switched back to the Wurmslayer/Sap, I had no problems keeping agro. I tried this several times over about 2 hours, and it was very consistent. Anyone have any insight into this?<br>
<br>
I admittedly know very little about how all this works yet... maybe its a monk thing I don't know. But I just thought it was interesting that I noticed such a difference. Also if anyone has any suggestions for weapons 1k+ I could use the input...<br>
<br>
Thanks,<br>
Glamdrin Foehammer<br>
Xegony <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/utalicmoore.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Talic Moore</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://forums.interealms.com/ranger/images/icons/Yin_Yang.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Hero of the Realms</span><br>  Posts: 563<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/30/01 10:25:16 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://eyesonff.com/ff1/fighter.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Agro/taunt</span><hr size=1> I'm not touching another Wurmslayer post.<br>
<br>
